<h5 id="ibookstore">iBookstore</h5>
<p>Apple's storefront for EPUBs and iBooks.</p>
<h5 id="icon">Icon</h5>
<p>A small symbol or picture used in a <strong>Graphical User Interface (GUI)</strong>. The icons on the computer screen represent programs or files, e.g. a picture of a painter's palette might represent a program used for drawing and editing pictures, and a picture of a book with a question mark on its cover might represent the text of a manual or a help file.</p>
