<h5 id="streaming">Streaming</h5>
<p>Playing audio or video in real time from a website. In order to play streaming multimedia files you need a specific plug-in program that links in with your browser and plays the file as it is transmitted rather than downloading it to your computer first. Streaming requires a broadband connection to the internet since multimedia files are not stored on your computer but played in a continuous stream direct from the computer where they are stored.</p>
